flowchart TD
    A[gitpulse] --> B[Load Config]
    B --> C{Which command?}

    C -->|scan| D[Find all repos]
    C -->|standup| E[Find all repos]
    C -->|cleanup| F[Find all repos]
    C -->|watch| G[Find all repos]
    C -->|overview| H[Find all repos]

    D --> I[Check status per repo]
    I --> J[Print status table]

    E --> K[Get commits by author + date]
    K --> L[Print standup report]

    F --> M[Find merged / stale branches]
    M --> N{User confirms?}
    N -->|yes| O[Delete branches]
    N -->|no| P[Skip]

    G --> Q[Run scan]
    Q --> R[Sleep interval]
    R --> Q

    H --> S[Aggregate stats]
    S --> T[Print health score]